Depends: bash (>=4), bluez, jq, xscreensaver
Description: BTPLS - Bluetooth Proximity Screen Locker.
 BTPLS - Bluetooth Proximity Screen Locker - Bluetooth proximity sensor and screen locker. Screensaver is launched based on bluetooth proximity value and treshold. A device's MAC address specified in configuration file.

